value.0: A slight breeze ripples the water's surface, giving your reflection a life of its own.
The water tumbles into the pool below, the sound of its fall marking a cheerful note.
The sacred waters of this fountain enable resting.
The energy emitting from this powerful Bindstone touches your very soul. Created by long dead masterwizards of the long forgotten Academy of High Magery, these stones can be found all over the realm.
